{
  "id" : "api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator",
  "title" : "ViewChildrenDecorator",
  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"viewchildrendecorator\">ViewChildrenDecorator</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\">@angular/core</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChildrenDecorator</a> } from <a href=\"api/core\">'@angular/core'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts#L257-L297\">core/src/metadata/di.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<h2 id=\"interface-overview\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"15ffnfvjx5orhxzfayretyfy4\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>接口概览</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChildrenDecorator</a> { \n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator#call\">(selector: Type&lt;any&gt; | Function | string, opts?: {...}): any</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator#new\">new (selector: Type&lt;any&gt; | Function | string, opts?: {...}): ViewChildren</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4n0dzb8dsvz53ivhgaj2xhl3f\">ViewChildren 装饰器/构造函数的类型。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6wlkjzi8qn2nmotlcsllhxmq8\">参见 \n<a href=\"api/core/ViewChildren\"><code>ViewChildren</code></a>。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-members\">\n  <h2 id=\"members\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e62kgm2ztk7rgk6auybfiv91o\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>成员</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"call\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">(selector: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&lt;any&gt; | Function | string, opts?: {\n    read?: any;\n}): any</code-example>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1dn5n7hufo1f1lle9xc8mozoy\">你可以使用 ViewChildren 从视图 DOM 中获取与选择器匹配的元素或指令的 \n<code><a href=\"api/core/QueryList\"><code>QueryList</code></a></code>。每当添加、删除或移动子元素时，查询列表都会更新，并且查询列表的变化可观察者会发出一个新值。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3jgjji9dxo8xaw3cqexem3pa0\">视图查询在调用 \n<code>ngAfterViewInit</code> 回调之前设置。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"958p250s4a4gqxdqtti9sbuqo\"><strong>元数据属性</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6ixorlow9hdb02vbe8pe45lr\"><strong>selector</strong> - 用于查询的指令类型或名称。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eaqly4chu86q2wost59mk0wes\"><strong>read</strong> - 从查询的元素中读取不同的令牌。</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1as6sssxkbpwanrxvy471wt78\">让我们看一个例子：</p>\n<code-example>\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>, <a href=\"api/core/QueryList\" class=\"code-anchor\">QueryList</a>, <a href=\"api/core/ViewChildren\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChildren</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: 'pane'})\nexport class Pane {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>() id: string;\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'example-app',\n  template: `\n    &lt;pane id=\"1\"&gt;&lt;/pane&gt;\n    &lt;pane id=\"2\"&gt;&lt;/pane&gt;\n    &lt;pane id=\"3\" *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"shouldShow\"&gt;&lt;/pane&gt;\n    \n    &lt;button (click)=\"show()\"&gt;Show 3&lt;/button&gt;\n       \n    &lt;div&gt;panes: {{serializedPanes}}&lt;/div&gt; \n  `,\n})\nexport class ViewChildrenComp implements <a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a> {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/ViewChildren\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChildren</a>(Pane) panes: <a href=\"api/core/QueryList\" class=\"code-anchor\">QueryList</a>&lt;Pane&gt;;\n  serializedPanes: string = '';\n\n  shouldShow = false;\n\n  show() { this.shouldShow = true; }\n\n  ngAfterViewInit() {\n    this.calculateSerializedPanes();\n    this.panes.changes.subscribe((r) =&gt; { this.calculateSerializedPanes(); });\n  }\n\n  calculateSerializedPanes() {\n    setTimeout(() =&gt; { this.serializedPanes = this.panes.map(p =&gt; p.id).join(', '); }, 0);\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<p><strong>npm package</strong>: <code>@angular/core</code></p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"new\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">new (selector: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&lt;any&gt; | Function | string, opts?: {\n    read?: any;\n}): <a href=\"api/core/ViewChildren\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChildren</a></code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core\n - api/core/AfterViewInit\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/QueryList\n - api/core/Type\n - api/core/ViewChildren\n - api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator#call\n - api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator#description\n - api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator#interface-overview\n - api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator#members\n - api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator#new\n - api/core/ViewChildrenDecorator#viewchildrendecorator\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts#L257-L297\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\n-->"
